# Password Cracking Tools

Niche kuch popular password cracking tools ki list di gayi hai:

* **John the Ripper**: Ek fast password cracker jo kai types ke passwords ko support karta hai.
* **Hashcat**: Duniya ka sabse fast CPU/GPU based password recovery tool.
* **Hydra**: Ek bahut hi fast network login cracker jo kai protocols (SSH, FTP, etc.) ko support karta hai.
* **Aircrack-ng**: Wireless network passwords ko crack karne ke liye best tool suite.
